    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/b31672bb507955b3100aa0b5a75951a9.avif?t=1768868609\" width=600 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿起相机，在这款治愈系第一人称模拟游戏中释放你的摄影热情 —— 每一张照片都能定格独一无二的故事！作为一名崭露头角的摄影师，你将打造专属梦想工作室，为模特定制个性造型，在每一个镜头里捕捉极致可爱的瞬间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁全维度定制自由：混搭百变发型、玩转多彩妆容，从日常休闲风到动漫元气穿搭，海量服饰库任你搭配。精调每一处细节：以第一视角调整模特的身姿、手势与神态，精准拿捏理想氛围，更可切换自由相机模式，寻觅最佳拍摄角度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >承接客户委托任务赚取奖励，解锁丰富拍摄道具与限定服饰，持续扩充你的创意工具箱。这不止是拍照 —— 你还能培养模特的专属气质，建立默契羁绊，让每一次拍摄都成为一场欢乐协作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >依托 Steam 创意工坊，创意边界无限延伸：分享你的得意作品，下载社区大神创作的内容，与全球摄影爱好者并肩交流。此外，完成 14 项 Steam 成就，解锁属于你的摄影大师勋章！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是想寻找轻松治愈的创意出口，还是热爱动漫风格、渴望打造萌系场景的玩家，《摄影师》都能为你带来温馨沉浸的体验，让你的艺术构想照进现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/6530f56870940b0912b05c028447518e.poster.avif?t=1768868609\" width=710 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/6530f56870940b0912b05c028447518e.webm?t=1768868609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/6530f56870940b0912b05c028447518e.mp4?t=1768868609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第一人称工作室搭建与摄影玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度定制系统：发型、妆容、服饰、姿势、神态全掌控</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由相机视角，拍摄角度灵活切换</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >客户委托任务，解锁海量道具与服饰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模特养成与互动玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持 Steam 创意工坊与 14 项 Steam 成就</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 种语言适配（英语、简体中文、繁体中文、俄语、法语、意大利语、德语、西班牙 - 西班牙语）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/563c085d0c9cf336912e166db5122110.poster.avif?t=1768868609\" width=730 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/563c085d0c9cf336912e166db5122110.webm?t=1768868609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1562800/extras/563c085d0c9cf336912e166db5122110.mp4?t=1768868609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
